{"word":"G3819 - πάλαι - pálai - pal'-ahee - Any while","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πάλαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">pálai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pal'-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Any while</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"அப்பொழுதே, அதற்குள்ளே - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"1. of old"},{"paragraph":"2. long ago"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Probably another form for <a href=\"#/G3825 - πάλιν - pálin - pal'-in/3825\">G3825</a> (through the idea of <i>retrocession</i>); (adverbially) <i>formerly</i>, or (relatively) <i>sometime since</i>; (elliptically as adjective) <i>ancient:</i> - any while, a great while ago, (of) old, in time past.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G3819/3819\">G3819</a>, <a href=\"#/G3820/3820\">G3820</a>, <a href=\"#/G3821/3821\">G3821</a>, <a href=\"#/G3822/3822\">G3822</a>"}]}